title: [Highpark Lane, Gardens]
description: Highpark Lane approaches a heavily wooded area to the east, where the dark trunks of ancient trees punctuate the woodland landscape beneath a canopy of green.  The carefully tended lawn is dotted with several teak benches, and statuary stands in reverent attitudes here and there.

Highpark Lane approaches a heavily wooded area to the east, where the dark trunks of ancient trees punctuate the woodland landscape beneath a shadowy canopy of green.  The carefully tended lawn is dotted with the shadows of several teak benches, and moonlit statuary stands in reverent attitudes here and there.
